OL,3,CNigel Farage demands Reform be allowed
OL,4,Cto nominate peers to the House of Lords
OL,6,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has
OL,7,Fcalled on the government to allow him
OL,8,Fto nominate candidates to become peers
OL,9,Fin the House of Lords.
OL,11,FIn a letter to Prime Minister Keir
OL,12,FStarmer, the Reform UK leader said a
OL,13,F"democratic disparity" in the upper
OL,14,Fchamber needed to be addressed.
OL,16,FReform won five seats in the 2024
OL,17,Felection and currently has four MPs,
OL,18,Fincluding Farage. They also control
OL,19,Ften councils across England.
