OL,3,CNigel Farage demands Reform be allowed
OL,4,Cto nominate peers to the House of Lords
OL,6,FFarage argues smaller parties like the
OL,7,FGreens, who have the same number of
OL,8,FMPs and control fewer councils, have
OL,9,Ftheir own lords, creating the
OL,10,F"disparity" to which he refers.
OL,12,FIn his letter, first reported by The
OL,13,FTimes, Farage writes: "My party
OL,14,Freceived over 4.1 million votes at the
OL,15,Fgeneral election in July 2024."
