OL,3,CNigel Farage demands Reform be allowed
OL,4,Cto nominate peers to the House of Lords
OL,6,FFarage has previously called for
OL,7,Freforming the House of Lords, arguing
OL,8,Fin February that a smaller chamber was
OL,9,Fneeded.
OL,11,FResponding to Farage's demands on
OL,12,FFriday morning, Defence Secretary John
OL,13,FHealey told LBC: "I'm not sure that
OL,14,Fparliament's going to benefit from
OL,15,Fmore Putin apologists like Nigel
OL,16,FFarage, to be honest."
OL,18,FAsked whether that accusation was "a
OL,19,Fbit strong", Healey said: "Look at
OL,20,Fwhat he's said about Russia, look at
OL,21,Fwhat he's said about Putin in the past.
