OL,6,FSpeaking from Cambridgeshire on
OL,7,FFriday, Liberal Democrat Leader Ed
OL,8,FDavey said Nigel Farage "seems to be
OL,9,Fmostly interested in Nigel Farage".
OL,11,F"The fact that he's focusing on how he
OL,12,Fcan get his mates into the House of
OL,13,FLords says all you need to know about
OL,14,FNigel Farage," he added.
OL,16,FHe went on to accuse the Reform leader
OL,17,Fof neglecting to talk about the real
OL,18,Fissues of security and economy,
OL,19,Finstead focusing on how he could
OL,20,F"feather his own nest".
